sbygoogle\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 300px; height: 250px;\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-9716398444039739\" data-ad-slot=\"4680411731\"></ins>\r\n<script>\r\n   (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\r\n</script></p>\r\n<p>Below an example:</p>\r\n\r\n[php]\r\n $number = 5;\r\n $fact   = 1;\r\n while($number &gt; 0) {\r\n    $fact = $fact * $number;\r\n    $number--;\r\n }\r\n  echo $fact; // Output 120\r\n[/php]\r\n\r\n<p>In above, we wrote a program to generate the factorial of 5 and the factorial of 5 came 120.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\'shr\'>That\'s it!. Please share your thoughts or suggestions in the comments below.</p>','Write a program to generate a factorial of any number in php','','inherit','closed','closed','','114-revision-v1','','','2019-09-12 20:36:48','2019-09-12 15:06:48','',114,'https://nexladder.com/blog/114-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(307,1,'2019-09-12 20:36:57','2019-09-12 15:06:57','<p>In this article, We\'ll see how to get file extension in php.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We\'ll use <code>pathinfo()</code> function to get the file extension.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><code>pathinfo()</code> function returns information about a file path: either an associative array or a string, depending on options.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-center\"><script async src=\"//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js\"></script><br />\r\n<!-- Ad 4 --><br />\r\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 300px; height: 250px;\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-9716398444039739\" data-ad-slot=\"4680411731\"></ins><br />\r\n<script>\r\n   (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\r\n</script></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Below an example:</p>\r\n\r\n[php]\r\n $filename = &quot;report.xls&quot;;\r\n $ext = pathinfo($filename, PATHINFO_EXTENSION);\r\n echo $ext; // Output xls\r\n[/php]\r\n\r\n<p class=\'shr\'>That\'s it!. Please share your thoughts or suggestions in the comments below.</p>','How to get file extension in php ?','','inherit','closed','c